============
Introduction
============

Compilation Notes for Sorcery on Linux. Updated 19th July 2026. My Development 
Environment is Ubuntu 26.04 LTS.

================
Tested Compilers
================

Currently tested using:

- GCC 15.2
- CMake 3.22+

The project targets C++23 and should compile with any reasonably recent GCC
supporting C++23 (GCC 14 or later is recommended).

=======
Git LFS
=======

Sorcery stores artwork using Git LFS.

Before cloning the repository, install Git LFS and enable it:

	git lfs install

Failure to do so will result in placeholder files being checked out instead of
the artwork contained within gfx/.

Please note as of 4th July 2026, I have replaced the master branch with the 
sdl/imgui branch and have archived the older SFML-based version of the code. 
That branch is no longer updated, and will also be archived in the near future.

